						 <div style="display:none"><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/nav%3Aside/styleFrame.html?bhl" name="typeFrame"></iframe></div> <div class="anom-bar-container item-5922 clear-3 euclid {$secondary-class} vlam 警告 {$american} lang-cn"> <div class="anom-bar"> <div class="top-box"> <div class="top-left-box"><span class="item"><span class="lang-cn">项目编号：</span><span class="lang-tr">項目編號：</span></span><span class="number">5922</span></div> <div class="top-center-box"> <div class="bar-one"></div> <div class="bar-two"></div> <div class="bar-three"></div> <div class="bar-four"></div> <div class="bar-five"></div> <div class="bar-six"></div> </div> <div class="top-right-box"> <div class="level"><span class="lang-cn">等级</span><span class="lang-tr">等級</span>3</div> <div class="clearance"></div> </div> </div> <div class="bottom-box"> <div class="text-part"> <div class="main-class"> <div class="contain-class"> <div class="class-category"><span class="lang-cn">收容等级：</span><span class="lang-tr">收容等級：</span></div> <div class="class-text">euclid</div> </div> <div class="second-class"> <div class="class-category"><span class="lang-cn">次要等级：</span><span class="lang-tr">次要等級：</span></div> <div class="class-text">{$secondary-class}</div> </div> </div> <div class="disrupt-class"> <div class="class-category"><span class="lang-cn">扰动等级：</span><span class="lang-tr">擾動等級：</span></div> <div class="class-text">vlam</div> </div> <div class="risk-class"> <div class="class-category"><span class="lang-cn">风险等级：</span><span class="lang-tr">風險等級：</span></div> <div class="class-text">警告</div> </div> </div> <div class="diamond-part"> <div class="danger-diamond"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/classification-committee-memo">备忘录链接</a><br /> <div class="arrows"></div> <div class="octagon"></div> <div class="quadrants"> <div class="top-quad"></div> <div class="right-quad"></div> <div class="left-quad"></div> <div class="bottom-quad"></div> </div> <div class="top-icon"></div> <div class="right-icon"></div> <div class="left-icon"></div> <div class="bottom-icon"></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <p><strong>特殊收容措施：</strong>基金会网络爬虫ANGELA.aic将监控互联网和新闻媒体中突发心衰竭的案例，尤其关注多人在共用网络空间时死亡的案例。ANGELA.aic将定期查询ORPHEUS.aic收集到的聊天室记录，搜索类似信息并扫描其中有无潜在认知危害。</p> <p><strong>描述：</strong>SCP-5922是一条认知危害性信息，能对感知到它的对象诱发心脏衰竭。SCP-5922是在2020年9月22日的一起事件后被发现，该事件造成11名年龄在18到26岁之间的人员于7分钟内死亡。发现所有对象死亡时都正在某一线上聊天室进行交流。</p> <p>于2020/09/25，收容团队找到了涉及此事故的非异常平民。Mr. Castro被发现处于严重的心理紧张状态，已对其进行记忆删除并提供悲痛咨询。</p> <hr /> <p><strong>附录5922.01：</strong>聊天记录抄录</p> <div class="discord"> <div class="messages-panel"> <div class="messages-group"> <div class="messages"> <div class="message yissod"> <div class="icon"></div> <div class="body"> <div class="userblock"> <div class="user-name">Yissod</div> <div class="msg-time">22/09/2020</div> </div> <div class="content">天空</div> </div> </div> <div class="message beans"> <div class="icon"></div> <div class="body"> <div class="userblock"> <div class="user-name">beans</div> <div class="msg-time">22/09/2020</div> </div> <div class="content">每回都该死</div> </div> </div> <div class="message tohos"> <div class="icon"></div> <div class="body"> <div class="userblock"> <div class="user-name">Tohos</div> <div class="msg-time">22/09/2020</div> </div> <div class="content">各位</div> </div> </div> <div class="message prosp"> <div class="icon"></div> <div class="body"> <div class="userblock"> <div class="user-name">PROSP</div> <div class="msg-time">22/09/2020</div> </div> <div class="content"><span class="at_mention">@Yissod</span> 我他妈发誓</div> </div> </div> <div class="message tohos"> <div class="icon"></div> <div class="body"> <div class="userblock"> <div class="user-name">Tohos</div> <div class="msg-time">22/09/2020</div> </div> <div class="content">各位<br /> 看这个<br /> 你们现在要有意呼吸</div> </div> </div> <div class="message nico"> <div class="icon"></div> <div class="body"> <div class="userblock"> <div class="user-name">NICO NICOOOO</div> <div class="msg-time">22/09/2